=Episode 5=

16
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:31,159
This woman shall not remain.

17
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:34,640
Or Heaven will punish
those in the Prince's Manor,

18
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,640
and misfortune will never cease.

19
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,799
Since marrying Prince Heir,

20
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,439
I've never shown even an ounce

21
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:53,079
of defiance against the family's rules.

22
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,480
Yet I'm subjected to such persecution.

23
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,319
Grandmother,

24
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,840
do you believe such baseless rumors?

25
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:12,319
Your Ladyship,

26
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,360
look at what's happening to Shiyi!

27
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,360
Can you bear to risk Shiyi's life

28
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:18,520
and the entire Lu family's future?

29
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,120
What a pitiful display!

30
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,000
Utter nonsense!

31
